b'[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)  \n[English](../gita/bg14.htm)  \n[Previous](bgs13.htm)  [Next](bgs15.htm)\n\n* * *\n\nXIV. atha caturda\xc5\x9bodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5.  \n(gu\xe1\xb9\x87atrayavibh\xc4\x81gayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)  \n  \n\xc5\x9br\xc4\xabbhagav\xc4\x81n uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \npara\xe1\xb9\x83 bh\xc5\xabya\xe1\xb8\xa5 pravak\xe1\xb9\xa3y\xc4\x81mi j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81nam  \nuttamam  \nyaj j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81tv\xc4\x81 munaya\xe1\xb8\xa5 sarve par\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 siddhim ito gat\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n14.1  \n  \nida\xe1\xb9\x83 j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81nam up\xc4\x81\xc5\x9britya mama s\xc4\x81dharmyam \xc4\x81gat\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nsargepi nopaj\xc4\x81yante pralaye na vyathanti ca 14.2  \n  \nmama yonir mahad brahma tasmin garbha\xe1\xb9\x83 dadh\xc4\x81my  \naham  \nsa\xe1\xb9\x83bhava\xe1\xb8\xa5 sarvabh\xc5\xabt\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 tato bhavati bh\xc4\x81rata 14.3  \n  \nsarvayoni\xe1\xb9\xa3u kaunteya m\xc5\xabrtaya\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa\xe1\xb9\x83bhavanti y\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nt\xc4\x81s\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 brahma mahad yonir aha\xe1\xb9\x83 b\xc4\xabjaprada\xe1\xb8\xa5 pit\xc4\x81 14.4  \n  \nsattva\xe1\xb9\x83 rajas tama iti gu\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 prak\xe1\xb9\x9btisambhav\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nnibadhnanti mah\xc4\x81b\xc4\x81ho dehe dehinam avyayam 14.5  \n  \ntatra sattva\xe1\xb9\x83 nirmalatv\xc4\x81t prak\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bakam an\xc4\x81mayam  \nsukhasa\xe1\xb9\x85gena badhn\xc4\x81ti j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81nasa\xe1\xb9\x85gena c\xc4\x81nagha 14.6  \n  \nrajo r\xc4\x81g\xc4\x81tmaka\xe1\xb9\x83 viddhi t\xe1\xb9\x9b\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81sa\xe1\xb9\x85gasamudbhavam  \ntan nibadhn\xc4\x81ti kaunteya karmasa\xe1\xb9\x85gena dehinam 14.7  \n  \ntamas tv aj\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81naja\xe1\xb9\x83 viddhi mohana\xe1\xb9\x83 sarvadehin\xc4\x81m  \npram\xc4\x81d\xc4\x81lasyanidr\xc4\x81bhis tan nibadhn\xc4\x81ti bh\xc4\x81rata 14.8  \n  \nsattva\xe1\xb9\x83 sukhe sa\xe1\xb9\x83jayati raja\xe1\xb8\xa5 karma\xe1\xb9\x87i bh\xc4\x81rata  \nj\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81nam \xc4\x81v\xe1\xb9\x9btya tu tama\xe1\xb8\xa5 pram\xc4\x81de sa\xe1\xb9\x83jayaty uta 14.9  \n  \nrajas tama\xc5\x9b c\xc4\x81bhibh\xc5\xabya sattva\xe1\xb9\x83 bhavati bh\xc4\x81rata  \nraja\xe1\xb8\xa5 sattva\xe1\xb9\x83 tama\xc5\x9b caiva tama\xe1\xb8\xa5 sattva\xe1\xb9\x83 rajas tath\xc4\x81  \n14.10  \n  \nsarvadv\xc4\x81re\xe1\xb9\xa3u dehesmin prak\xc4\x81\xc5\x9ba upaj\xc4\x81yate  \nj\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81na\xe1\xb9\x83 yad\xc4\x81 tad\xc4\x81 vidy\xc4\x81d viv\xe1\xb9\x9bddha\xe1\xb9\x83 sattvam ity uta  \n14.11  \n  \nlobha\xe1\xb8\xa5 prav\xe1\xb9\x9bttir \xc4\x81rambha\xe1\xb8\xa5 karma\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81m a\xc5\x9bama\xe1\xb8\xa5 sp\xe1\xb9\x9bh\xc4\x81  \nrajasy et\xc4\x81ni j\xc4\x81yante viv\xe1\xb9\x9bddhe bharatar\xe1\xb9\xa3abha 14.12  \n  \naprak\xc4\x81\xc5\x9boprav\xe1\xb9\x9btti\xc5\x9b ca pram\xc4\x81do moha eva ca  \ntamasy et\xc4\x81ni j\xc4\x81yante viv\xe1\xb9\x9bddhe kurunandana 14.13  \n  \nyad\xc4\x81 sattve prav\xe1\xb9\x9bddhe tu pralaya\xe1\xb9\x83 y\xc4\x81ti dehabh\xe1\xb9\x9bt  \ntadottamavid\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 lok\xc4\x81n amal\xc4\x81n pratipadyate 14.14  \n  \nrajasi pralaya\xe1\xb9\x83 gatv\xc4\x81 karmasa\xe1\xb9\x85gi\xe1\xb9\xa3u j\xc4\x81yate  \ntath\xc4\x81 pral\xc4\xabnas tamasi m\xc5\xab\xe1\xb8\x8dhayoni\xe1\xb9\xa3u j\xc4\x81yate 14.15  \n  \nkarma\xe1\xb9\x87a\xe1\xb8\xa5 suk\xe1\xb9\x9btasy\xc4\x81hu\xe1\xb8\xa5 s\xc4\x81ttvika\xe1\xb9\x83 nirmala\xe1\xb9\x83 phalam  \nrajasas tu phala\xe1\xb9\x83 du\xe1\xb8\xa5kham aj\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81na\xe1\xb9\x83 tamasa\xe1\xb8\xa5 phalam  \n14.16  \n  \nsattv\xc4\x81t sa\xe1\xb9\x83j\xc4\x81yate j\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81na\xe1\xb9\x83 rajaso lobha eva ca  \npram\xc4\x81damohau tamaso bhavatoj\xc3\xb1\xc4\x81nam eva ca 14.17  \n  \n\xc5\xabrdhva\xe1\xb9\x83 gacchanti sattvasth\xc4\x81 madhye ti\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadhanti  \nr\xc4\x81jas\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5  \njaghanyagu\xe1\xb9\x87av\xe1\xb9\x9bttisth\xc4\x81 adho gacchhanti t\xc4\x81mas\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 14.18  \n  \nn\xc4\x81nya\xe1\xb9\x83 gu\xe1\xb9\x87ebhya\xe1\xb8\xa5 kart\xc4\x81ra\xe1\xb9\x83 yad\xc4\x81 dra\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xad\xc4\x81nupa\xc5\x9byati  \ngu\xe1\xb9\x87ebhya\xc5\x9b ca para\xe1\xb9\x83 vetti madbh\xc4\x81va\xe1\xb9\x83 sodhigacchhati  \n14.19  \n  \ngu\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81n et\xc4\x81n at\xc4\xabtya tr\xc4\xabn deh\xc4\xab dehasamudbhav\xc4\x81n  \njanmam\xe1\xb9\x9btyujar\xc4\x81du\xe1\xb8\xa5khair vimuktom\xe1\xb9\x9btam a\xc5\x9bnute 14.20  \n  \narjuna uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nkair li\xe1\xb9\x85gais tr\xc4\xabn gu\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81n et\xc4\x81n at\xc4\xabto bhavati prabho  \nkim\xc4\x81c\xc4\x81ra\xe1\xb8\xa5 katha\xe1\xb9\x83 cait\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83s tr\xc4\xabn gu\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81n ativartate 14.21  \n  \n\xc5\x9br\xc4\xabbhagav\xc4\x81n uv\xc4\x81ca  \n  \nprak\xc4\x81\xc5\x9ba\xe1\xb9\x83 ca prav\xe1\xb9\x9btti\xe1\xb9\x83 ca moham eva ca p\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87\xe1\xb8\x8dava  \nta dve\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadi sa\xe1\xb9\x83prav\xe1\xb9\x9btt\xc4\x81ni na niv\xe1\xb9\x9btt\xc4\x81ni k\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x85k\xe1\xb9\xa3ati 14.22  \n  \nud\xc4\x81s\xc4\xabnavad \xc4\x81s\xc4\xabno gu\xe1\xb9\x87air yo na vic\xc4\x81lyate  \ngu\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81 vartanta ity eva yovati\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadhati ne\xe1\xb9\x85gate 14.23  \n  \nsamadu\xe1\xb8\xa5khasukha\xe1\xb8\xa5 svastha\xe1\xb8\xa5 samalo\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xad\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bmak\xc4\x81\xc3\xb1cana\xe1\xb8\xa5  \ntulyapriy\xc4\x81priyo dh\xc4\xabras tulyanind\xc4\x81tmasa\xe1\xb9\x83stuti\xe1\xb8\xa5 14.24  \n  \nm\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81pam\xc4\x81nayos tulyas tulyo mitr\xc4\x81ripak\xe1\xb9\xa3ayo\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nsarv\xc4\x81rambhaparity\xc4\x81g\xc4\xab gu\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81t\xc4\xabta\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa ucyate 14.25  \n  \nm\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 ca yovyabhic\xc4\x81re\xe1\xb9\x87a bhaktiyogena sevate  \nsa gu\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81n samat\xc4\xabtyait\xc4\x81n brahmabh\xc5\xaby\xc4\x81ya kalpate 14.26  \n  \nbrahma\xe1\xb9\x87o hi prati\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadh\xc4\x81ham am\xe1\xb9\x9btasy\xc4\x81vyayasya ca  \n\xc5\x9b\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bvatasya ca dharmasya sukhasyaik\xc4\x81ntikasya ca 14.27  \n  \n  \n\n* * *\n\n[Next: XV. atha pa\xc3\xb1cada\xc5\x9bodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (puru\xe1\xb9\xa3ottamayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)](bgs15.htm)\n\n'